## Static hosting: email is handled by PHP. After you upload the `out/` folder:
## 1. Copy public/contact-config.example.php to contact-config.php on the server
##    (same directory as index.html and contact.php — usually public_html).
## 2. Fill in SMTP_* values (Hostinger mailbox SMTP works well).
